<div class="container">

  <h4>To enable or disable add-ons, edit the Gemfile.plugins file and restart the application.</h4><br/><br/>
  
  <h2>1. Edit /dradisframework/Gemfile.plugins</h2><br/>
  <p>Scan the contents of the Gemfile.plugins file to find the lines relevant to the plugin(s) you want to enable or disable.</p>
  <p><strong>To enable a plugin:</strong> uncomment the relevant lines.</p>
  <p><strong>To disable a plugin:</strong> comment the relevant lines.</p><br/>
  <h2>2. Update and restart the application</h2>
  <code>    $ bundle install</code>
  <p>After restarting the application, you should be ready to go with your add-ons correctly enabled or disabled.</p><br/><br/>
